 Jude Okoye Gifts Himself a Mansion for Christmas ended 2020 in a grand style by getting himself a new mansion. According to him, the mansion is his Christmas gift for the year. Okoye invested millions of naira in building the mansion. Okoye shared photos of the newly-built home situated in Parkview, Ikoyi area of Lagos state on Instagram. He captioned the photos: ‘Let’s say Xmas gift came early. #realestate #realinvestment #builtfromscratch.’ View this post on Instagram A post shared by jude okoye (@judeengees)